iDirectDebit,provides,payment,processing,services,in,the,UK,and,abroad,including,paper,and,paperless,Direct,Debits,credit,cards,debit,cards,checks,and,postal,orders,The,iDirectDebit,API,allows,service,users,to,integrate,sign,up,functionality,into,third,party,applications,The,API,supports,the,creation,of,a,customized,Direct,Debit,sign,up,wizard,and,allows,Direct,Debit,Instructions,DDIs,to,be,easily,managed,and,maintained,It,provides,users,with,control,over,branding,payer,sign,up,Direct,Debit,collections,edits,confirmation,and,reports,The,API,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,XML,Full,documentation,is,not,publicly,available